high_descs: Walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk across the room to the small black table that is against the wall to the right of the fireplace.
Pick up the pencil that is closest to the keys on the small black table.
Turn left and walk over to the couch, then turn left again and walk across the room, hang a left and walk up to the large wooden table.
Put the pencil on the grey plate that is on the large wooden table next to the two white vases.
Pick up the grey plate with the pencil on it.
Turn left and walk towards the fire place, then turn left and walk up to coffee table.
Put the grey plate with the pencil on it on the coffee table just below the watch.
anns.task_desc: Put a grey plate with a pencil on it on the coffee table.

high_descs: Walk in the direction of the door, hang a left at the stairs, walk toward the dining room table, hang a left toward the direction the fireplace, stop at the brown table to the right of the fireplace.
Pick up the middle pencil on the brown table.
Turn around and walk to the dining room table at the end with the two white vases and brown tray.
Place the pencil inside the tray.
Pick up the tray with the pencil in it.
Turn towards your left and walk in the direction of the fireplace, hang a left at the front of the purple couch, turn toward the table with drawers across from the front of the couch.
Place the tray at the left front of the table with drawers and in front of the wrist watch and remote control.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a pencil, place it in a tray, move the tray to the table in front of the couch

high_descs: Turn to the left and go across the room, then left again to find the small table along the wall.
Pick up the pencil from the short side of the table.
Carry the pencil and turn around, then left at the dining table.
Place the pencil on the plate that is in the middle of the table.
Pick up the plate from the middle of the table.
Carry the plate and pencil and turn to the left and then the right to find the coffee table.
Place the plate and pencil on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Move a plate and pencil to the coffee table.
